data.description: Fantastic home for sale. Located in a small gated community with community pool and quick freeway access. Just outside the Summerlin masterplan but with all the access to Summerlin and Red Rock. The oversized lot is very spacious, low maintenance backyard. The home features 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms and a 2 car garage. Gorgeous tile throughout the first floor, along with a master bedroom downstairs. Vaulted ceilings, fireplace in living room, cozy kitchen and upgraded master bathroom with walk in shower. Freshly painted and new carpet makes this home ready for it's next owner.
